nodes.text: This Gotal, during the Death Seed crisis of 14 ABY, was the female captain of the Quarantine Enforcement Cruiser Lycoming, a cruiser belonging to the Coruscant Institute. She also had a Gotal chief medical officer named Tuuve with her. The captain received a distress call from the Empyrean which she responded to and discovered and arrested a group of Gamorrean scavengers led by Ugmush. Later, she also arrested Yarbolk Yemm, an investigative journalist. She ordered the captive to be thrown out of an airlock to protect Loronar Corporation, which turned out to be responsible for the Death Seed outbreak.
